How to run a simple test with SiII 

From test/SiII/. :

1/ compile the code
cd ../../f90
mv Makefile Makefile_std
cp ../tests/SiII/Makefile_SiII Makefile
make 
cd ../tests/SiII

2/ run
../../f90/CreateDomDump params_CDD.dat

3/ link python scripts
ln -s ../../py/*py .

4/ start the ipython notebook plotSpec.ipynb
-> follow steps to generate parameter files, run PhotonsFromSourceModel and rascas-serial, and plot the results. 


